title: HUMAN EVENTS DAILY: NOV 4 2021- FBI ARRESTS SOURCE OF STEELE DOSSIER
description:
On today’s episode, The FBI arrests source of Steele Dossier, The family that runs Kenosha is targeting Kyle Rittenhouse, President Joe Biden issues federal vaccine mandate, and Iran says IRGC foiled U.S Navy’s attempt to steal its oil tanker in the Persian Gulf. 


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
